~ blinky_dialogue
if GameManager.balloon_unlocked
	Blinky: I hope you're enjoying the balloon! I'm so glad my friends are coming to visit now!
else if GameManager.pinky and GameManager.pokey and GameManager.clyde and GameManager.inky
	Blinky: You found all of them! I'm so grateful, here take this balloon you earned it!
	do GameManager.balloon_unlocked = true
else
	Blinky: I miss my friends, I think they've all got lost in this labyrinth. If you see them, please ask them to come find me.
	do GameManager.ghost_hunt_started = true
=> END